      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UTTER MADNESS (1) was a little disappointing last start at Angle Park when 8th (30.98) over 530m. Has an impeccable record here at this journey having won all three wins. Ready to return to form. FANTASTIC SPIKE (6) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (30.77) in a Grade 5 at Angle Park. Form at the trip sound including 14 wins. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and three minor placings from six starts. Leading chance. MOSCOW CHICK (8) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 455m behind Wraps (26.18) in a Grade 4/5. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. RITZA WOTTON (2) placed out of the same box last time out - worth some thought.",
